ote><blockquote><blockquote>係<br />\n跟足法例佢炒你唔洗理由</blockquote><br />\n唔識咪出聲啦,要畀理由架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢up唔出d咩合理理由可以問佢追討終止僱傭金</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得無錯<br />\n所以叫人即走<br />\n要有原因<br />\n否則老闆要賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔好傻啦<br />\n你咪試下去勞工處追囉<br />\n老細是但比個理由都收裁判官皮啦<br />\n你唔係覺得政府可以叉到隻手去私人市場度呀？<br />\n我做左6年HR 未見過有老細比足通知期被人告得入</blockquote><br />\n補充多少少，我上過勞資審裁處打不合理解僱case<br />\n個官兜口兜面同我講，你比足通知期，你話佢樣衰解僱佢都冇問題<br />\n當然有冇歧視係另外一個話題"},{"pid":"a108e7641df5afd8f870d74c4cbaae5cc24b26f8","tid":459720,"uid":55614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講<br />\n我做錯既係唔肯做2個人既野<br />\n早2個星期支氣管炎入左醫院一個星期，一出院就叫我走</blockquote><br />\n入院就收信有得拗喎<br />\n不過有成兩個月慢慢hea 豪比佢啦"},{"pid":"57eae5c01da42f6d86b9a79ecbc67bc6245e8a14","tid":459720,"uid":141081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:38:38.000Z","msg":"邊hea 邊搵工兩個月啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8593d4950980f904b7ee5223a9d07dcaf78d190","tid":459720,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理論上唔可以話佢炒你, 炒就係即走, 而家最多叫和平分手</blockquote><br />\n咁係好事<br />\n和平分手有ref letter"},{"pid":"34aaf2e204f995a9de58fa77a8d82d343d262829","tid":459720,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18633925e0851a4114b7da98e1d9356adc0ea0f","tid":459720,"uid":65406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊hea 邊搵工兩個月啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大假病假拎盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre